data.description: This luxurious coastal residence sits on a double lot in the desirable non-rental gated community of BellaMar along Scenic Hwy. 30A. With over 8,493sf, this 6 bedroom, 6.5 bath home allows for a large family to gather together, then escape to their own private suites at the end of the day. This one owner home was built with high impact windows and doors and the first level is all concrete construction. Large room sizes and 11' ceilings give this home a substantial feel, along with an elegant foyer with a grand staircase leading to the 2nd floor. An elevator services both levels of the home. The 2BR/2BA guest house w/office sits next to the pool.  The backyard boasts lush greenery and a Beverly Hills style 20x40 ft. saltwater pool with a huge covered loggia in which to entertain in style.
